Installing or updating to the latest version of the AWS CLI on ubuntu machine .

1 . Update the Package List.
     apt update 
2 . Installed (Best Method – Official AWS CLI v2)
     curl "https://awscli.amazonaws.com/awscli-exe-linux-x86_64.zip" -o "awscliv2.zip"
     unzip awscliv2.zip
     ./aws/install
3 . Verify Installation 
      aws --version 
    Example output : aws-cli/2.34.4 Python/3.13.11 Linux/6.6.87.2-microsoft-standard-WSL2 exe/x86_64.ubuntu.24
4 . Configure AWS
      aws configure 
                  AWS Access Key ID
                  AWS Secret Access Key
                  Default region name
                  Default output format
